data.description: Here's a chance for an investor/or buyer to see the possibilities of bringing a 2-unit building back to life! Sure it needs some renovation to restore its colors to its glamorous state, update the kitchen, and the bathrooms, add new floors. The renovation list becomes yours to create!! Current hardwood floors can be restored. Property is currently owner occupied. Garden unit is not occupied, and requires some renovation. Spacious 1st. floor unit with large kitchen, and view of back yard. Attic can be converted into additional living space.
